{"tid":422316,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯：連「外邊的人」也開始愛中國，醒來吧！不要懵閉閉拒絕去愛！","createTime":"2017-10-03T03:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T07:01:21.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0ddb7a0eb6485ed746b9a6caf54a8e0383f7d379","tid":422316,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171003/s00001/c1a6ddb3ffd7586dc8d82efd5ba5c445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171003%2Fs00001%2Fc1a6ddb3ffd7586dc8d82efd5ba5c445.jpg&h=26919b35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n建制派立法會議員何君堯於facebook，以逾百字談及「突然愛國」，認為揶揄者是受「鸦（鴉）片」餘毒影響，「中毒」太深。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯昨日於facebook分享外國人翻唱台灣組合S.H.E.《中國話》YouTube片段，他留言時提及「突然愛國」，指「香港有些人，將愛國當成罪過，當你表明心迹之時，他們會揶揄你突然愛國，叫你是共匪」，認為這些人一直被過去200年的「鸦（鴉）片」餘毒影響，「中毒太深，至今仍搞不清自己是誰！」<br />\n<br />\n何君堯又說，連「外邊的人」也開始愛中國，「醒來吧！不要懵閉閉拒絕去愛！」<br />\n<br />\n另外，本身是嶺大校董的何君堯，發表10點聲明回應嶺大學生針對其「殺無赦」言論進行的行動，呼籲學生不要被人誤導、 利用，又強調自己「從良心出發」、「有法可依」，質疑「（學生）怎可要求何君堯辭去嶺南校董呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171003/s00001/1506998975636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171003%2Fs00001%2F1506998975636&d=FvcdFaugKY56zwVCqh3gAvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=5373276a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171003%2Fs00001%2F1506998975636&h=9d17b873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171003/s00001/1506998975636</a>"},{"pid":"5291976008d1b2e46f0046bf03d279498aaeae6a","tid":422316,"uid":48022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:22:10.000Z","msg":"用埋殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas